<view class="page">
  <view class="section">
    <text class="title">记录</text>
    <text class="subtitle">记录饮食、运动和体重，首页与数据页会自动同步。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="section efficiency-grid">
    <view class="efficiency-card" bindtap="goFavorites"><text class="efficiency-title">常吃食物</text><text class="efficiency-desc">优先选择常用食物</text></view>
    <view class="efficiency-card" bindtap="goRecent"><text class="efficiency-title">最近记录</text><text class="efficiency-desc">复用最近重量</text></view>
    <view class="efficiency-card" bindtap="goTemplates"><text class="efficiency-title">饮食模板</text><text class="efficiency-desc">整餐快速添加</text></view>
    <view class="efficiency-card" bindtap="goCalendar"><text class="efficiency-title">打卡日历</text><text class="efficiency-desc">查看连续记录</text></view>
  </view>

  <view class="section list">
    <view class="card record-card" bindtap="goDietDetail">
      <text class="record-title">今日饮食</text>
      <text class="record-desc">查看、编辑、删除今日饮食，支持复制昨日饮食。</text>
    </view>
    <view class="card record-card" bindtap="goFoodSearch">
      <text class="record-title">添加饮食</text>
      <text class="record-desc">添加到早餐、午餐、晚餐或加餐。</text>
    </view>
    <view class="card record-card" bindtap="goExercise">
      <text class="record-title">运动记录</text>
      <text class="record-desc">新增、编辑或删除运动记录。</text>
    </view>
    <view class="card record-card" bindtap="goWeight">
      <text class="record-title">今日体重</text>
      <text class="record-desc">保存或更新今天的体重记录。</text>
    </view>
    <view class="card record-card" bindtap="goCustomFood">
      <text class="record-title">自定义食物</text>
      <text class="record-desc">创建常用食物，用于饮食记录。</text>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
